                  數學規劃                   

                     3學分3小時
                  





課程名稱
                    數學規劃                 
 英文課程名稱
                    Mathematics Programming                 
 中文課程概要
                    l 線性規劃之圖解和代數解，線性規劃之對偶，流動模式之線性規劃，網路式線性規劃，整數規劃，動態規劃，計畫程式表，排隊理論。 

 英文課程概要
                    l This course is designed mainly for graduate students. The objective of this course is to introduce the concepts of linear programming, duality, applications of linear programming, integer programming, dynamic programming, scheduling, and queuing theory. 







