 課程簡介 





　





課程名稱
數學規劃


授課對象
數學系三年級學生


預備知識




其他條件






The Simplex Method

Basic feasible solutions and pivoting operation,
Artificial variable,
Degeneracy and cycling,
Bland's rule,
Klee-Minty twisted cube model and efficiency.

The Duality theorem and dual simplex method

The weak duality theorem,
The strong duality theorem,
Negative transpose property and duality problem,
Farkas Lemma and duality theorem,
Sensitivity and parametric analysis.

Network flow

The Transportation Problem,
The Assignment Problem,
The Shortest-Path Problem,
The Maximum-Flow Problem.

Game theory    Interior point method




　




　

