Michael R. Garey and David S. Johnson. Computers and Intractability: A Guide to the Theory of NP-Completeness. W.H. Freeman. 1979. ISBN 978-0-7167-1045-5.  A6: MP1: INTEGER PROGRAMMING, pg.245.

